3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a technique to improve the performance of object boundary detection, which is an important task in AI. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image annotations and object detection, which are important tasks in multimedia analysis. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with improving the quality of image annotations, which can be useful in image retrieval tasks.
